title: Baker Mayfield, Jalen Ramsey, Aaron Donald, & Dak Prescott
itunes:title: Baker Mayfield, Jalen Ramsey, Aaron Donald, & Dak Prescott
description:
Colin discusses why Cleveland Browns QB Baker Mayfield will be starting soon, Jacksonville Jaguars CB Jalen Ramsey's recent comments about New England Patriots TE Rob Gronkowski, Los Angeles Rams DE Aaron Donald's new contract, and why the Dallas Cowboys need QB Dak Prescott. Guests include Al Michaels, Ryan Leaf, Greg Cosell, and Bucky Brooks.
